4,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時睇唔明本書up mud 9<br />\n會走去YouTube 搵 video 解釋<br />\n睇完YouTube 再睇番本書又明</blockquote><br />\n我朝早果陣睇得明<br />\n夜晚就會好似文盲咁理解唔到"},{"pid":"082d4cb03c9771525deace324060fcb72cd22648","tid":421864,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不停飲水保持頭腦清晰<br />\n睇15分鐘<span style=\"color: red;\">訓15分鐘</span></blockquote><br />\n係咪就咁閉目養神果隻都ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我好難訓得著"},{"pid":"80bcb5c3ec7e88a9b7c0f8cc8b5ecbc42052586e","tid":421864,"uid":7514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:10:27.000Z","msg":"打J<br />\n食煙"},{"pid":"c70ce4a3ed58d85dc0a2b1d91d200020466c002f","tid":421864,"uid":5077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"拎生果刀插大脾"},{"pid":"a22e6fe4e5388f4d0edb2b6759f258bc6d036a52","tid":421864,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:16:03.000Z","msg":"你有腦疲勞症狀嗎？測一測就知道！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-早晨總是想賴床，不想起床<br />\n-走路有氣無力，抬不起腿<br />\n-不想參加社交活動，只想窩在家當宅男宅女<br />\n-懶得講話，說起話來也有氣無力<br />\n-老是想當沙發馬鈴薯，坐下後就不想起來<br />\n-時常發呆發楞<br />\n-記憶力減退，時常忘東忘西</span><br />\n-頭暈、頭痛、耳鳴、易怒、煩躁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-眼睛疲勞，經常打哈欠</span><br />\n-食慾變差，討厭油膩，甚至會想添加多點調味料刺激味蕾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-不好入睡，睡眠品質變差</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-雙腳無力，休息時想把腳放在桌子上</span><br />\n<br />\n如果有上述2至4項情況時，代表你輕微疲勞，請多休息；有上述5至9項情況時，表示你中度疲勞了，關掉壓力的聯繫，讓自己放空；<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有10項以上表示你已經重度疲勞，也許還可能潛藏疾病，建議應馬上就醫檢查。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wellness.cigna.com.tw/wz/Health/Detailed/Mood?id=1067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwellness.cigna.com.tw%2Fwz%2FHealth%2FDetailed%2FMood%3Fid%3D1067&d=UuZ1iPTJC%2FYJcpizRsrAQDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=42f8db93\" target=\"_blank\">https://wellness.cigna.com.tw/wz/Health/Detailed/Mood?id=1067</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街，重度疲勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff6cc094b3959047298701b8caa190b70bbe333","tid":421864,"uid":39000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有腦疲勞症狀嗎？測一測就知道！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-早晨總是想賴床，不想起床<br />\n-走路有氣無力，抬不起腿<br />\n-不想參加社交活動，只想窩在家當宅男宅女<br />\n-懶得講話，說起話來也有氣無力<br />\n-老是想當沙發馬鈴薯，坐下後就不想起來<br />\n-時常發呆發楞<br />\n-記憶力減退，時常忘東忘西</span><br />\n-頭暈、頭痛、耳鳴、易怒、煩躁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-眼睛疲勞，經常打哈欠</span><br />\n-食慾變差，討厭油膩，甚至會想添加多點調味料刺激味蕾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-不好入睡，睡眠品質變差</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-雙腳無力，休息時想把腳放在桌子上</span><br />\n<br />\n如果有上述2至4項情況時，代表你輕微疲勞，請多休息；有上述5至9項情況時，表示你中度疲勞了，關掉壓力的聯繫，讓自己放空；<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有10項以上表示你已經重度疲勞，也許還可能潛藏疾病，建議應馬上就醫檢查。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wellness.cigna.com.tw/wz/Health/Detailed/Mood?id=1067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwellness.cigna.com.tw%2Fwz%2FHealth%2FDetailed%2FMood%3Fid%3D1067&d=UuZ1iPTJC%2FYJcpizRsrAQDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=42f8db93\" target=\"_blank\">https://wellness.cigna.com.tw/wz/Health/Detailed/Mood?id=1067</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街，重度疲勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味 我中晒係咪就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1a9c104c0730b3c0bf6315f9d42e9a7811c958","tid":421864,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:35:56.000Z","msg":"有冇讀書秘訣？"},{"pid":"28d893280c891b6fdef99545ebf7cbecb4989aba","tid":421864,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"一邊睇一邊讀會唔會好啲？<br />\n同埋個人會一句句子brief view一次再咬文嚼字一次 <br />\n以上係俾唔focus嘅時候用<br />\n有時會望完成頁都唔知自己睇左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"